data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious and inviting 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom ranch is a true gem. Three bedrooms are conveniently located on the main level, while an additional bedroom can be found in the basement. Enjoy the convenience of 2 full bathrooms on the main level and a half bath located in the basement. The basement is a versatile space with endless possibilities. It includes one bedroom and a half bath, making it ideal for guests, a home office, or a recreational haven. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, gas stove with ventless exhaust, and plenty of counter and cabinet space. The one-car garage is attached along with a double wide driveway. The back yard is fully fenced in and ready for outdoor activities. Schedule your showing today! Seller is open to paying part of Buyer concessions!
